AUDIO: 'PIW file. Metadata will be lost. Uh but that\'s that\'s uh all proprietary format we\'re using. &gt;&gt; So, if I understand this NVOL is what makes your PIW specifically suited for the Unreal high color accuracy'

[20:00] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'and applications. &gt;&gt; That\'s right. That\'s right. So, uh we are compatible with the OCIO, which is Open Color IO module of Unreal. This means that no matter'

